Package org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.datamodel

Class BaseDNDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.datamodel.BaseDNDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<BaseDNDescriptor>
    public class BaseDNDescriptor
extends Object
implements Comparable<BaseDNDescriptor>
    This class is used to represent a Base DN / Replica and is aimed to be used by the classes in the BackendTableModel class.
